```css
.navbar {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    background-color: #2c3e50;
    padding: 15px 30px;
}
.nav-links { display: flex; list-style: none; gap: 25px; }
.nav-links a { color: #ecf0f1; text-decoration: none; }
.nav-links a:hover { color: #3498db; }
```
space-between pushes logo and links to opposite ends; align-items: center vertically centers them.

```css
.card-container {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 20px;
}
.card {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 280px;
    background-color: #fff;
    border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 25px;
}
```
flex: 1 = equal growth; min-width: 280px prevents too-narrow cards; flex-wrap: wrap allows wrapping.
